  <brief_title>A Double-blind Placebo-controlled Study to Evaluate Larazotide Acetate for the Treatment of Celiac Disease</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Double-blind, Placebo-controlled Study to Evaluate the Efficacy and Safety of Different Doses of Larazotide Acetate for the Treatment of Celiac Disease</official_title>
  <sponsors>
